keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

unmap f
unmap F
unmap m
unmap t
unmap k
unmap <c-e>

map e LinkHints.activateMode
map E LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab

map s scrollDown
map S scrollPageDown
map j scrollDown
map J scrollPageDown

map w scrollUp
map W scrollPageUp
map k scrollUp
map K scrollPageUp

map h scrollLeft
map a scrollLeft
map l  scrollRight
map d scrollRight


map D nextTab
map L nextTab
map A previousTab
map H previousTab

map Z goBack
map C goForward
